HEADWORD: Multispiral
<hw>Mul`ti*spi"ral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Multi-</ets> + <ets>spiral</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Having numerous spiral coils round a center or nucleus; -- said of
the opercula of certain shells.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

